{
  "title": "Pickers",
  "href": "http://www.google.com/design/spec/components/pickers.html",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "intro",
      "html": "<p>Pickers provide a simple way to select a single value from a pre-determined set.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "article-list",
      "articles": [
        {
          "type": "article",
          "title": "Usage",
          "modules": [
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>On mobile, pickers are best suited for display in a <a href=\"http://www.google.com/design/spec/components/dialogs.html#dialogs-confirmation-dialogs\">confirmation dialog</a>. </p><p>For inline display, such as on a form, consider using compact controls such as <a href=\"http://www.google.com/design/spec/components/buttons.html#buttons-other-buttons\">segmented dropdown buttons</a>. </p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "article",
          "title": "Date pickers",
          "modules": [
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>A dialog picker is used to select a single date on mobile. </p><p>The selected day is indicated by a filled circle. The current day is indicated by a different color and type weight. </p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "figure-group",
                  "figures": [
                    {
                      "type": "figure",
                      "mediaType": "image",
                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0B3321sZLoP_HVWZOVkdRQlJEdDg/components_pickers_date1.png",
                      "caption": "<p>Date and year picker: Light theme, portrait</p>"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>Swipe left to right to navigate through the months. Touch the year in the title bar to transition to the year view.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "figure-group",
                  "figures": [
                    {
                      "type": "figure",
                      "mediaType": "video",
                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0B6Okdz75tqQsSm5KN1FNQXRFRDA/components_pickers_date_navigation_xhdpi_004.webm",
                      "caption": "<p>Date picker navigation</p>"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>The picker view adapts to the device&#x2019;s orientation. </p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "figure-group",
                  "figures": [
                    {
                      "type": "figure",
                      "mediaType": "image",
                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0B3321sZLoP_Hamc5d1k2SmhlV2c/components_pickers_date3.png",
                      "caption": "<p>Date picker: Light theme, landscape</p>"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>A dark theme picker can complement apps that have a dark theme.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "figure-group",
                  "figures": [
                    {
                      "type": "figure",
                      "mediaType": "image",
                      "src": "media/publish/material_v_4/material_ext_publish/0B3321sZLoP_HOTZoUE1VSGxvRFE/components_pickers_date4.png",
                      "caption": "<p>Date picker: Dark theme, portrait</p>"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>Landscape view of the dark theme picker.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "type": "figure-group",
